enum VXLIB_STATUS_NAME

The enumeration of all status codes.

Enumerator:
VXLIB_SUCCESS  No Error
VXLIB_ERR_FAILURE  Unspecified Error
VXLIB_ERR_INVALID_VALUE  Invalid parameter value
VXLIB_ERR_INVALID_TYPE  Invalid parameter type (VXLIB_data_type_e data_type)
VXLIB_ERR_INVALID_DIMENSION  Dimension parameter (width/height) is too big/small
VXLIB_ERR_NULL_POINTER  Unsupported null pointer condition
VXLIB_ERR_NOT_IMPLEMENTED  Parameter configuration is not supported/implemented
VXLIB_ERR_NOT_EQUAL_WIDTH_STRIDE  Stride should be equal to width * element size
VXLIB_ERR_NOT_ALIGNED_PTRS_STRIDES  Pointers and stride values are not aligned to documented value
VXLIB_ERR_NOT_ALIGNED_WIDTHS  Width values are not aligned to documented value
VXLIB_ERR_BUFFER_TOO_SMALL  Buffer size not large enough
